        "timestamp": "2020-05-02 14:24:22.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi,\n\nThis commit aims to refactor the CsarUtils::WriteArtifactDefinition function and to use Either as recommended by the best practices.\n\nThis refactoring required to break the `WriteArtifactDefinition` function in multiple smaller functions, as it was coded in a very imperative way which prevented getting the best of Either. The code is now simpler to read and to maintain. \n\nA test had to be removed (CsarUtils::testWriteArtifactDefinition) as the function it covered does not exist anymore. The new functions are covered by the other tests as shown by Sonar.\n\nThank you in advance for your help.\n\nFrancis.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
